  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Integrated Planning to Implement the CBD Strategic Plan and Increase Ecosystem Resilience to Climate Change</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project increased capacity to optimize land use planning to support biodiversity and climate change adaptation objectives. Through a combination of global reviews and in-country assessments, target countries were provided with advice, guidance, and assistance in demonstration activities.  The project results provided recommendations for legal planning tools. Policy dialogues ensured that the necessary political leadership can translate recommendations into implementation and sustained action in their countries. Knowledge products and tools were made available to a wider audience of decision makers and stakeholders. Visibility of results and lessons were ensured through participation and profiling of project progress and outcomes at key international forums.</narrative>
  </description>
